sed -stream editor,It is powerful command line tool used to search,find,replace insert ,delete or transform text in automated way.
To use of sed command,we can edit file without opening into the file

1.Replace text (substitution)
    sed 's/old text/new text/' <filename>.txt
    example:
        sed 's/banana/BANANA/g' fruits.txt   #g means all occurrence of the 
2.Delete lines
    sed '/banana/d' fruits.txt   #this command delete every line having the banana word
    
    To delete word at particular line 
        sed '3d' fruits.txt
        